 />\n<br />\n其實要幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外你地會唔會用msi個效能turbo mode, 係咪預設超vram</blockquote><br />\n幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命？<br />\n電子野一向撞手神，好難講<br />\n當你枱機都係80-90度<br />\n你latop做到咁既溫度仲想點</blockquote><br />\ndesktop唔會放隻手上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪要買厚機囉，隔熱做得好<br />\ngt72/73個種<br />\n最抵玩係gt72 1070個部"},{"pid":"2555c6f7c93cb35d49f89beba06f9ad93f86feff","tid":365443,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人用gs40?有冇keyboard問題/其他問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買呢部打機會手指鐵板燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5361cbdc7f9c6f0146d91c34640a9409301e665","tid":365443,"uid":65041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>參考下<br />\n<br />\nge63vr 7rf 新機<br />\nvram 6gb<br />\n左手好熱, 右手無乜feel, keyboard中間幾熱, 電池位暖暖地<br />\noverwatch推到頂, 開turbo風扇, cpu接近80度, gpu約75度<br />\n木枱面<br />\n<br />\n其實要幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外你地會唔會用msi個效能turbo mode, 係咪預設超vram</blockquote><br />\n幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命？<br />\n電子野一向撞手神，好難講<br />\n當你枱機都係80-90度<br />\n你latop做到咁既溫度仲想點</blockquote><br />\ndesktop唔會放隻手上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪要買厚機囉，隔熱做得好<br />\ngt72/73個種<br />\n最抵玩係gt72 1070個部</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係唔想太厚重，想要拎個中間既<br />\n<br />\n者係可以有少少暖手又唔太重咁樣囉"},{"pid":"fe65f30a15bcd1a1623cdd54036bf66bd7b475aa","tid":365443,"uid":81693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"用緊gs60<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  打機都真係幾熱，可以去到8x/90 度，散熱就一般，機背會勁辣手<br />\nqc 就我諗撞手神，我個部二手用咗兩年幾(rend 圖、打機) 依家都未壞，但當然比初初買返嚟無咁順<br />\n係粒電漲到機殻變咗型要換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重量就雖然機就輕但火牛係好q重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20eab54b4d9e3e638a83615fd00e562f3676a63b","tid":365443,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>參考下<br />\n<br />\nge63vr 7rf 新機<br />\nvram 6gb<br />\n左手好熱, 右手無乜feel, keyboard中間幾熱, 電池位暖暖地<br />\noverwatch推到頂, 開turbo風扇, cpu接近80度, gpu約75度<br />\n木枱面<br />\n<br />\n其實要幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外你地會唔會用msi個效能turbo mode, 係咪預設超vram</blockquote><br />\n幾熱先會影響cpu同gpu壽命？<br />\n電子野一向撞手神，好難講<br />\n當你枱機都係80-90度<br />\n你latop做到咁既溫度仲想點</blockquote><br />\ndesktop唔會放隻手上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪要買厚機囉，隔熱做得好<br />\ngt72/73個種<br />\n最抵玩係gt72 1070個部</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係唔想太厚重，想要拎個中間既<br />\n<br />\n者係可以有少少暖手又唔太重咁樣囉</blockquote><br />\n冇架喎，一係熱一係完全唔熱<br />\n再呵係買新既分隔設計<br />\nasus gx501個類"}]}